name: White T-Shirt Special!
description:
Get 100 or more white t-shirts with a 1 color print in 1 location for only $3.50 a shirt including your shipping and set-up fees! .. Your choice of 50/50 or 100% cotton shirts! .. If you wish to print a different color garment call 1.800.992.2491 to place an order OR e-mail us at: orders@bandprints.com
